            <trans-unit id="s1xr73Y" resname="e-portfolio.h1.description">
                <source>e-portfolio.h1.description</source>
                <target>
                    My name is {name}. I am { age } years old.
                    Let me tell you how it all began.
                    When I was young, I played video games on consoles such as Playstation 2, my first game console, and
                    then Playstation 3.
                    My father, who likes video games too, bought a gaming laptop.
                    He told me that the laptop is better for playing and that it was the future
                    because we can do more things.
                    One day, he made me try his favorite games and I remember how much I loved.
                    From that day, I bought my first desktop PC and I started to take an interest in computers,
                    both hardware and development.
                </target>
            </trans-unit>
